text: The canton of Calais-1 is an administrative division of the Pas-de-Calais department, in northern France. It was created at the French canton reorganisation which came into effect in March 2015. Its seat is in Calais.Décret n° 2014-233 du 24 février 2014 portant délimitation des cantons dans le département du Pas-de-Calais It consists of the following communes: #Bonningues-lès-Calais #Calais (partly) #Coquelles #Escalles #Fréthun #Hames- Boucres #Nielles-lès-Calais #Peuplingues #Pihen-lès-Guînes #Saint-Tricat #Sangatte ==References== Category:Cantons of Pas-de-Calais
